==English==
===Noun===
'''interoperability'''
#(''military'') the [[ability]] of dfferent [[force]]s to [[exchange]] [[service]]s so as to [[operate]] [[effectively]] [[together]]
#{{computing}} the ability of [[software]] [[system]]s running under different [[operating system]]s and on different [[hardware]] to exchange [[information]] using the same [[file]] [[format]]s and [[protocol]]s
#"Metering" the ability of using the same software to read different make of meter (electricity ,Water ,Gas,Heat etc)

